## 🔐 SECURITY

> **AI: Read this before touching auth, input handling, data access, or any user-facing boundary.**
> **Never implement a security-relevant feature without checking this section first.**

### Authentication model
_AI: How are users identified? Token type, session strategy, storage location._

- Auth method: — _(JWT / session cookie / OAuth / API key / other)_
- Token storage: — _(httpOnly cookie / localStorage / memory)_
- Token lifetime: — · Refresh strategy: —
