2024-01-20 — The payment webhook fires twice on sandbox. Production fires once. The
deduplication logic in paymentWebhook.controller.js:88 handles this but only if the
idempotency key is passed. Never test payment flows without it.

2024-02-03 — The `config/app.config.js` export is lazy-evaluated. Importing it at module
top level in tests causes env vars to be read before the test setup runs. Always import
inside the test function body or use jest's setupFiles.

